>\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"7cb5dff2c3fb4c4384f34ac4c94cad1943868bb5","tid":1119264,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:24:22.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00812c9780b4b3c987a6bd78cf801cb0ebe05e6d","tid":1119264,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cb5dff2c3fb4c4384f34ac4c94cad1943868bb5","tid":1119264,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:24:22.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9dc87ff04e62e28698c3df0c24941d3398c636","tid":1119264,"uid":218081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"飲酒可以減輕思考負擔"},{"pid":"a381edce044b53cc6627dc5fc4e117cb46543b40","tid":1119264,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:42:02.000Z","msg":"以前都試過類似情況,<br />\n其實同人講會好啲, 點都好過收收埋埋"},{"pid":"6331d8a8bf2999bbd57ad01829b1eff33a200561","tid":1119264,"uid":224831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f1cdd83dc8761bdf3bf2efde1e3a586e4c4e730","tid":1119264,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:49:51.000Z","msg":"我都唔想再亂諗野，<br />\n個腦控制唔到喺度諗好多負面野，一諗就唔停，<br />\n我唔想再冇啦啦流淚，<br />\n好攰，我覺得自己好麻煩，冇價值，冇人愛我<br />\n0存在意義。。。<br />\n搵人傾個個嫌我煩，<br />\n你冇耐性我寧願一開頭唔好理我。。<br />\n我好hurt"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"ching同另一半相處得唔開心？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5057e2dfe9761385408ddc823800977a380ff150","tid":1119264,"uid":127150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住我媽，佢月